<br>
Should I go LFG in PoV or in PoS? <br>
<br>
Input please, thanks all! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
