Antonius Bayle<br>
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=39733">Magelo</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=conjurer59>Conjurer59</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 42<br> <font color=#333333>(2/17/03 4:13:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=195.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: yes</span><hr size=1> Thanks all for your input. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Over the weekend I had the opportunity to enjoy the gentle attentions of Aer' Dar ( sp ), which is my way of misspelling the name of that crystalline dragon in PoV. This was a large-scale attempt to get a bunch of folks flagged, and it was ... interesting, lol.<br>
<br>
The first attempt turned into a disorganized Zergfest, and I ended up getting summoned by His Glassiness. He hits fairly hard, 1374 damage melee in one hit. But it was the add that killed me, and I was a bit annoyed to have survived the dragon only to be killed by a <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>bug</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
I was too tired to wait for round two, but I later learned that subsequent attempts had succeeded, and over 130 people were flagged as a result. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
The remainder of the weekend I hunted in the deserts of PoV and PoS. PoV had better experience, but PoS was more fun. Me, a 58 Mage, and a 58 BL 2-boxing a 60 cleric. BL was tanking and we had no problems with adds, for the most part.<br>
<br>
I still don't really know the zones yet, but it's nice to have finally played in them.<br>
